      "date": "2019-01-30 22:01:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews-patchless/3181/ : SUCCESS\n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/61514/ : SUCCESS",
